                    <div class="mainHd">International partnerships and affiliations</div>
                    <div class="textBox mb-20">
                        The Yemeni University of Science and Technology strongly believes in the importance of forming
                        joint
                        links of collaboration with both local and international organizations and higher education
                        institutions. The University has formed a number of relation with educational institutions at
                        the
                        local and international levels, and this cooperation has resulted in a beneficial exchange for
                        both
                        parties.
                        <br/>
                        <br/>
                        With special regards to student and staff-oriented programs, joint research, and joint graduate
                        and
                        undergraduate programs, the links of mutual collaboration between the University of Science and
                        Technology and higher education institutions in countries such as Malaysia, China and Turkey are
                        especially characterized by long-term commitment. Such strong relationship has been the product
                        of
                        the continuous provision of joint programs between such universities.
                        <br/>
                        <br/>
                        In addition, the University of Science and Technology seeks to organize regular inter-university
                        international conferences, with which it manages several academic initiatives through active
                        participation in organizations and the provision of many educational and administrative
                        services.
                    </div>
                    <div class="caHd">The University of Science and Technology presides the list of a number of local
                        and
                        international institutions as an effective international partner, and contributor to a number of
                        medical, and educational institutions including the following:
                    </div>
